This directory is checked by build_component_map.py as a fallback location
for images referenced in AIC docs but not present in their source-relative
paths.

To override a missing image, drop a file named exactly like the source
markdown's reference (e.g. aic_overview.png). The generator picks it up
on next run.

Example: ~/Documents/aic/docs/overview.md has `![](../../media/aic_overview.png)`
which doesn't resolve (no ~/Documents/aic/media/ directory exists).
Drop aic_overview.png here to override.
